divs: Sighting Detailsi heard a jet pass overhead . i glanced up at it,while i was looking at the jet i saw what looked like a large box tumbling. at first i thought it was falling, but it did not seem to be losing altitude. i watched for a minute or two then went to get binoculars. when i got back, only about 20-30 seconds,i could not find it again.i guess i am reporting this to see if anyone else saw the same thing. i am 52 and this is only the second time in my life i saw somthing that i did not understand what it was. it really looked like a large refrigator box but it was very small. a asprin would cover it at arms length. i just cant shake the idea that i might have seen somthing un-explainable
